# VeggieRoulette Project Rules

## Design Style

- **Theme**: Earth tones theme
- **Background**: #365441 (Dark Green)
- **Primary Headers**: #2C4A34 (Dark Green)
- **Accent/Buttons**: #C85E51 (Terracotta)
- **Rounded corners**: 2xl or 3xl

## Code Rules

- Use `FlatList` for all scrolling lists
- Use strict Mock Data arrays at the top of files (e.g., `const DATA = [...]`) so backend team can replace them easily later
- Add `// TODO:` comments where API calls should happen
- Use file-based routing (Expo Router)

## Tech Stack

- React Native
- Expo Router
- NativeWind (Tailwind CSS)
- Lucide Icons

